Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani mo nai tadatada tsudzuku sora
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing is endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani hitotsu te ni todokanai yōna
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hi no biru no sukima kara mieta gaitō ni
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,600)}And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Comment: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{OP ED border}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You still adhere to that manner of pushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Winner - Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, with this victory Mr. Otonashi \Nhas earned the right to be promoted to Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:25.46,Default,,0,0,20,,{\fade(800,700)\an8\c&HFBFDFE&\bord1\shad2\blur2\3c&H586348&\4c&H657C54&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\4a&H00&\fscx117\fscy88}Episode 12\N {\fs92}Bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still winning merely by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come soon enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Such high spirits. \NDid you hit Big after Renchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In that terms, you can say it's ten Renchans at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You won that much but took no prizes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.87,0:02:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No... About that... I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't... \NWere you actually drunk when it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Sorta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a long way off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, any progress with development history materials?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All the materials relate to a certain period, so arranging them proved a bit tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stuck figuring out the relations?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That sheet is what I came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So it's between generations 1.5 and 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. \NYou covered 23 manufacturers here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see where your quest for knowledge brings you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think a coffee shop owner \Nhas such a dire need for materials on pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't cover all the manufacturers after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you already asked the Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In Oumi's storage room, there are only models of under 10 years old. It's generation 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.03,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I became interested in pachislot \Nis to cognize Ginya's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just can't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as it is fun for me, \NI don't think it's the same for Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, this way, \NI'm only straying further away from Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is there something on my face I need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How about taking a day off today? \NI'd like to give you another lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't get any food the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already scheduled for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say what happens the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I be mad about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I just... thought you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case you have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I quite do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.75,Song,,0,0,0,,Unknown caller
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Daiba. \NCan you talk? {TODO: Might as well be "You're a little late"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How come you have my number?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your resolve to play against me \Nis still unswerving?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it is! Did you finally feel like facing me \Nafter seeing yesterday's game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yesterday's game?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we have one game?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on whether the owner allows it. \NHowever, we should do it before 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,When I have the details, I'll call you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute more. \NCan I ask you a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your villa from back then, {TODO: false flag, nothing to do here :)}\Ncan you give me an interview there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,An interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take pictures of the machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will just take photos, \NI don't mind one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Preferably, I want to do it ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, tomorrow at 1 pm, I will be waiting at the villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you planning to get the owner's permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Permission has just been granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can finally play against Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I must win at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What was this all about - \Nthe yesterday's game and facing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday in the parlor I played against a guy next to me\Nand he happened to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he is facing me next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I interviewed this guy previously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He also has a friend collecting lots of old machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying, that's how it really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone say you are lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to also bring me to that villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As your kindred spirit, \NI should by all means visit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that! \NIt's a private exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening. \NPlease don't ask for such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that \Nafter what I just heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just forget what you heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, put it on my tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave just yet! {TODO: Going home so soon?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that? \NHe wanted to eat together with us, didn't he? {TODO: No idea. Like, at all. "Together have a meal isn't it?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, how about you eat a dinner together with me, instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For-re-al.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, we will have two rice omelets. \NA Dinner Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to this point, it was generation 1.5. \NNot a lot of it was preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Further down this row, \Nit's generation 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's generations 1 and 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Generation 2 is on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Generation 2 release followed a profound revision of standards, persisting up to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them look like the contemporary designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the end of generation 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on it's generation 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, that friend of yours sure is fond of his omnipotence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a vast collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.22,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, this is the Slothium owner's villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe, this will be remade into museum \Nand put on exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you get permission from owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our game is appointed at 5 pm tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow at 5 pm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, shall we head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This feeling... \NI had it only once. {TODO: Might as well be "Everyone was around..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Cherry Blossoms at Night {TODO: Remove?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:09:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with Yozakura Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time we came here, \Nit caught your attention as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozakura Gen 1?{/Ichigo?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who designed this machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The designer is Shinbashi Kojiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbashi Kojiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here... {Might as well be "It was there..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's work in such a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is all that ghost machine bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that Yozakura Ichigo thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He is my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbashi Kojiro is your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to finish that machine, \Ndad abandoned our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fushina, don't you think it's one amusing kink of fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy was in relation to Yozakura Ichigo all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the reason \Nhe cannot lift that burden off his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinks and snacks are at your disposal.\NPlease help yourselves to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me announce the rules \Nof the current special game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You will receive 50 starting coins. \NThose may be replenished up to 10 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Time limit is 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,12 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have any problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For the duration of the game, \Nno one except the three of us is allowed to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let us decide on the machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My opponent can choose of his own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The game starts any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be playing against you today \Nwith all due earnestness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit me with your best performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I do that every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Game starts in 5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,4. 3. 2. 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I must certainly win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way. \NIf I keep it up, I will hit you hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a Renchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.41,0:12:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By the sounds of it, you're doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it going on your side, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just warming up. \NThe night is still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how I'm gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not catching up on me this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He left the office early, \Nso I was sure it's for a date with Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Date, you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At what time did he leave the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,About 4 in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be playing pachislot somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,About that, he has indeed been busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at Ginya, I think \Nthere is nothing else in his head besides pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. One does not write an article without extensive knowledge of pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't get why is it imperative to become obsessed with pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is playing against others also required to write an article?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Against others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He is competing against others in pachislot. \NRight, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much myself, but he competes with his friends in who carries out more foods, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, this is all for the sake of a job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I have this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bar screwed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you are already past your peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite. I am just approaching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cretin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... \NWhy did I start losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are trying to storm it by force again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of fighting the rough waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the sandy beach flirts with them before returning them to the sea. {For CPS's sake dropped the "as I told you" part}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You are facing the endless rough waves head-on \Ntrying to stop the tide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time storming it by brute force.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Until one day the waves crush you to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sandy beach does the opposite to the cliff. \NIt never tries to stop the waves, playing with them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It lets the waves caress it before returning them to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In accordance with your heart, machine can either become a devil, or a kindly goddess, smiling at you from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, pachislot machine is a mirror \Nreflecting the slotter's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror, reflecting heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to focus on the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... \NWhy do you keep sabotaging against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit sabotaging my game!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In such a state, the goddess \Nwill never bestow you with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you know about it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror, reflecting heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in my heart, dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hate my dad. \NThat is why I had to turn my hatred towards pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I had never felt any kind of hatred to my father in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have 2 hours left. \NNever give up until the very end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that at least resembles the sandy beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:18:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba, pachislot is a whole lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fushina... is that \Nwhat you have been seeing as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner is Mr. Daiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a fairly enjoyable game.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:20:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we play against each other again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep winning and climbing up to me. \NIn other words, it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't know for sure \Nif I loved my dad or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he is still alive, \NI want to meet him.
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
