Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:\NOlder brother, younger sister
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will\Nstop the time.
